# LD example layout

## Control docks (bottom panels)

```html
<div class="ld-panel">
  <div class="ld-card">
    <div class="ld-card-body">
      <h3 class="ld-panel-title">Control Panel</h3>
      <div class="ld-sections">…</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
```

## Status readouts (viewport HUDs)

```html
<div class="ld-hud ld-hud-top-right">undo: 0 | redo: 0</div>
<div class="ld-hud ld-hud-top-left ld-hud-passive">transform: idle</div>
```

- `.ld-hud-passive` — overlay must not block viewport interaction
- `.ld-hud-narrow` — cap width (`max-w-xs`)
